    <section id="visibility">
        <h2>5. Build visibility</h2>
        <p>Every build has a visibility setting under your control:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Private</strong> (default) — visible to you only;</li>
            <li><strong>Public</strong> — visible to every visitor of the site, signed in or not;</li>
            <li><strong>Link sharing</strong> — accessible to <strong>anyone who has the link</strong>, without an account: only share the link with people you trust.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            You can change a build's visibility or delete it at any time. Deletion removes the
            build from the site, including for people holding the link.
        </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="hx-rule">

